channel.title: Quick Question About Auto Cache DL'er
channel.description:
Alriqht, so i've set up my auto cache downloader, but im not sure if it is riqht. Could somebody take a look at this and tell me what is wrong? It's still currently downloading the cache, but idk why it says that in the cmd box.
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2rz9p8n.png[/img]

item.title: Quick Question About Auto Cache DL'er
item.dc:creator: @thuqs_range2 thuqs range
item.description:
@thuqs_range2 wrote:

[quote=“RiiPiiNFtW, post:2, topic:432528”]Just ignore it. As long as it is dling the cache and unzipping and only saying that when its dling its fine.

The load methods are before the else to download the cache. The errors should be sent before or during the cache being dled.[/quote]

Alright, thank you very much.
I’ve been trying to get a auto cache downloader working for the last week now, but i’ve been trying to .rar the file instead of .zip lol, finnaly got it.
